266
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,950
We're begging you...

267
00:35:23,950 --> 00:35:26,160
Save us...

268
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:28,750
Save us...

269
00:35:28,750 --> 00:35:30,650
Save us...

270
00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:32,500
Save us from here...

271
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:34,340
What are you doing?!

272
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,680
Behave!

273
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:38,800
Squat!

274
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:41,510
Behave! I'm telling you to behave!

275
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:43,310
Squat well!

276
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:56,850
Heshi!

277
00:35:57,470 --> 00:36:01,390
Heshi, have you seen Gu Xiaowu?

278
00:36:01,390 --> 00:36:04,490
You scared away Gu Xiaowu this quickly?

279
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:11,130
Look! Isn't your beloved coming right now?

280
00:36:11,130 --> 00:36:14,390
Xiaowu! Where did you go?

281
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:17,710
I thought you left. You scared me.

282
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:20,040
I was roaming around the place; looking for a person.

283
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:21,790
Looking for who?

284
00:36:22,610 --> 00:36:24,330
That's right, Brother Heshi.

285
00:36:24,330 --> 00:36:28,950
That... Have you heard of a person called Batuer?

286
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:30,930
Why are you asking about him?

287
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:36,420
A few months ago, I met him. He wanted to buy tea from me.

288
00:36:36,420 --> 00:36:39,520
Hence, this time, I brought a load of good tea,

289
00:36:39,520 --> 00:36:41,830
but I haven't seen him since.

290
00:36:42,660 --> 00:36:47,180
Don't mention him anymore. A few days ago, he was captured by the Western Border Protectorate General Office.

291
00:36:47,180 --> 00:36:49,120
What happened?

292
00:36:49,120 --> 00:36:51,850
Isn't it because of some feud with the Li Empire?

293
00:36:51,850 --> 00:36:54,760
Otherwise, we wouldn't be keeping our grievances to ourselves.

294
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:59,080
Our brother got captured, but we can't even get revenge for him.

295
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:01,120
We feel oppressed.

296
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:03,880
What feud? This severe?

297
00:37:03,880 --> 00:37:07,250
Okay, don't worry. With the Little Princess around,

298
00:37:07,250 --> 00:37:10,640
you still fear that your tea leaves won't get sold?

299
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:11,930
You talk too much.

300
00:37:11,930 --> 00:37:14,780
Xiaowu, you haven't eaten yet. Right? Let's go.

301
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:45,100
What exactly is in this basket?

302
00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:48,570
Look for yourself.

303
00:37:53,290 --> 00:37:57,170
Clothes? For me?

304
00:37:57,170 --> 00:38:00,800
It's so cold here and you people from the Central Plains have very weak health.

305
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:03,550
If you get sick, no one will care for you.

306
00:38:09,290 --> 00:38:14,420
Do you know that in the Central Plains, girls cherish their feet like they were their lives.

307
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:18,050
Aside from their husbands, they cannot be seen by anyone else.

308
00:38:18,050 --> 00:38:20,270
Then what will happen if someone sees them?

309
00:38:24,870 --> 00:38:26,920
Then you marry her.

310
00:38:29,100 --> 00:38:31,140
Didn't you hear my grandfather?

311
00:38:31,140 --> 00:38:35,080
Only the person who kills the white-eyed wolf king can marry me.

312
00:38:37,380 --> 00:38:43,530
Let me ask you. As long as that person can kill the white-eyed wolf king, regardless of who he is, you will marry him?

313
00:38:43,530 --> 00:38:45,130
Of course!

314
00:38:45,130 --> 00:38:49,400
My grandfather's word cannot be unsaid. How can I let him go back on his words?

315
00:38:54,830 --> 00:38:56,440
But he said

316
00:38:56,440 --> 00:39:00,510
that in this world, there's no one who is able to kill the white-eyed wolf king.

317
00:39:07,740 --> 00:39:09,840
Gu Xiaowu,

318
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:15,940
will you kill the white-eyed wolf king for me?

319
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:27,390
What can I do since I already saw your feet?

320
00:39:32,370 --> 00:39:34,090
Wait for me.

321
00:39:38,890 --> 00:39:40,560
Oh right!

322
00:39:42,390 --> 00:39:44,650
Your breakfast.

323
00:39:46,340 --> 00:39:48,430
I prepared it for you.

324
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:57,450
Not properly pulling the cart!

325
00:39:57,450 --> 00:39:59,380
- You couldn't even pull a cart?
- We were wrong.

326
00:39:59,380 --> 00:40:03,250
You're wrong? Wrong! Wrong! Wrong!

327
00:40:03,250 --> 00:40:05,150
Stop!

328
00:40:07,160 --> 00:40:08,840
Princess.

329
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:12,800
What crime did they commit that you have to keep hitting them?

330
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,220
Princess, they are slaves.

331
00:40:14,220 --> 00:40:16,690
They are captured prisoners from the Central Plains.

332
00:40:16,690 --> 00:40:19,720
We treat our captured prisoners as slaves!

333
00:40:20,430 --> 00:40:23,920
- Mula, go back and admonish your slaves.
- Yes.

334
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:28,290
Cousin, slaves are still people. How could you treat them like that?

335
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:32,560
Xiaofeng, A'Du is looking for you.

336
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:33,810
A'Du?

337
00:40:33,810 --> 00:40:36,180
That's right. Go and see what she wants.

338
00:40:38,970 --> 00:40:41,450
I'll be back in a moment. Wait for me.

339
00:40:51,210 --> 00:40:55,660
Did Khan Tömür tell you to send me away?

340
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:04,340
Okay, then help me give something to Xiaofeng.

341
00:41:04,340 --> 00:41:06,100
Okay.

342
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:10,690
A'Du!

343
00:41:12,390 --> 00:41:14,330
What's up? You were looking for me?

344
00:41:14,330 --> 00:41:15,670
I just got a new pot of good wine.

345
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:17,640
Princess, let's go and try it.

346
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:19,180
Let's go!

347
00:41:33,390 --> 00:41:35,420
It smells really good.

348
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:41,410
Let me go and get Gu Xiaowu,

349
00:41:41,410 --> 00:41:43,620
